quran[170]{c,v,t}:
  11,6,"Ur illi lweêc di tmurt, mebla ma illa ôôeéq is ar Öebbi. Issen tanezdu$t is, tanîelt is. Meôôa, di Tezmamt ipbegginen"
  11,7,"D Neppa i Ixelqen tamurt akked igenwan di sdis wussan. Asgeld iS illa $ef waman. A kwen Ijeôôeb anwi segwen ara ixedmen ayen ilhan, sennig wiyav. Ma tenniv: \"ih, kunwi a d tekkrem deffir tmeppant nnwen\", wid ijehlen, war ccekk, a d inin: \"ayagi, kan, d ssêur n ûûeê"
  11,8,"Ma Neswexxeô asen aâaqeb ar imir ipwassnen, war ccekk, a d inin: \"d acu iT iîîfen\"? Ass ideg ara ten id iawev, day illa wa ara ten iveôôfen segs? Ad asen izzi wayen i$ef pmmaâliken"
  11,9,"Ma Nesêess i umdan aêunu nne¨£, sinna, Nekkes as t, atan ad iayes, ad ijhel"
  11,10,"Ma Nesêess as l$it, deffir twa$it i t innulen, atan ad yini: \"fukkent felli lemêayen\", d$a, neppa, ad ifôeê, ad izux"
  11,11,"Kkes ed wid iûebbôen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan. I widak ssmaê akked tikci meqqwôen"
  11,12,"Ahat teppaoav kra n wayen ik ed ippuweêêan. Pzemmiven yis idmaren ik mara qqaôen: \"a lemmer i s d irs ugerruj, ne$ idda d, yides, lmelk\"! Keçç d aneddaô kan. Öebbi d Awkil n yal cci"
  11,13,"Ne$ ad inin: \"isnulfa t id\". Ini: \"awit ed, s usnulfu, mraw n tsuôtin am neppa. Naâôet ayen iwumi tzemrem, war Öebbi, ma tessawalem tidep"
  11,14,"Ma ur awen d rran ara, cfut ar irs ed kan s tussna n Öebbi, ar ur illi ôebbi siwa Neppa. Ihi, ma kunwi d imvuâen"
  11,15,"I wid ib$an tameddurt n ddunit akked ôôêuê is, a Nkafi, degs, igiten nnsen, ur asen Ntekkes"
  11,16,"Widak, ur ppafen, di laxeôt, siwa times. Ad i$li wayen ûenâen degs; inqev wayen xeddmen"
  11,17,"Day win iddan d ubeggen, s$uô Mass is, u immal as t unagi s$uôeS…? U, uqbel is, Tazmamt n Musa, d nnhaya u d aêunu. Wigi umnen yis. Win i p inekôen, seg ikubar, ppaâud is d times. Ur ppili di ccekk fellas. Neppa, ih, d tidep s$uô Mass ik. Maca, tegwti n medden ur ppamnen"
  11,18,"Anwa idensen sennig win id isnulfan tikerkas $ef Öebbi? Wigi a d rsen i Mass nnsen. A d inin inagan: \"d wigi i iskaddben $ef Mass nnsen\". Day Öebbi ur Ixezzu yara imednas"
  11,19,"I isîixxiôen seg ubrid n Öebbi, i t issarmen d uâwij, nitni ur uminen s laxeôt"
  11,20,"Wigi, ur sfunnugen di tmurt, ur asen illi bab, war Öebbi. Fellasen aâaqeb ar wayev. Ur zmiren ad slen, ur pwalin"
  11,21,D wigi i isxesôen iman nnsen. Itelf iten wayen d snulfuyen
  11,22,"Ur illi ccekk, ih, nitni ad xesôen, di laxeôt, sennig wiyav"
  11,23,"Ih, wid iumnen, u xeddmen ayen ilhan, u unzen aS i Mass nnsen, widak d at Loennet, degs ad wekkôen"
  11,24,"Amedya n snat n trebbuyaâ am uder$al, uâééug, akked win ipwalin, win isellen. Day âadlen sin imedyaten agi? Day ur d tesmektayem ara"
  11,25,"Ni$ Nuzen ed Nuê i ugdud is: \"nek d aneddaô nnwen ipbegginen"
  11,26,"iwakken ur tâabdem siwa Öebbi. Nek ugaded aâaqeb fellawen, ass aqeôhan"
  11,27,"Nnan imvebbôen, wid ijehlen, seg ugdud is: \"keçç, $uône$, d amdan am nekwni. Nwala, d ôôdiyen nne$, kan, war ameyyez, i k ivefôen. Ur nwala s wacu i $ tifem. Xaîi, nêesb ikwen d ikeddaben"
  11,28,"Inna: \"a yagdud iw! Acu twalam ma ddi$ d ubeggen n Mass iw? Ifka yi d aêunu s$uôeS. Idreg fellawen. Day a t nêeppem fellawen, ma kunwi tugim t"
  11,29,"A yagdud iw! Ur awen ssuture$ ayla, ilmend is; taqdiât iw ar Öebbi kan. Ur ppara$, nek, wid iumnen. S tidep, ad mlilen d Mass nnsen. Maca, nek wala$ kwen d agdud ur nessin"
  11,30,"A yagdud iw! Acu ara yi isellken seg ufus n Öebbi, lemmer i ten rri$ akin, day ur d tesmektayem ara"
  11,31,"Ur awen qqaôe$: $uôi lexzayen n Öebbi. Ur ssine$ tabavnit. Ur qqaôe$: nek d lmelk. Ur qqaôe$ i wid êeqôent wallen nnwen: ur asen Ippak ara Öebbi lxiô, d awez$i. Yif akw Öebbi akken Iéôa, i illan deg iman nnsen. Mulac ad ili$ seg imednas"
  11,32,"Nnan: \"a Nuê! Ni$ tnamrev a$, tessugtev a$ anamer. Ihi, awi ya$ d ayen i $ tâahdev, ma tessawalev tidep"
  11,33,"Inna: \"d Öebbi kan ar awen t id Iawin, ma ihwa yaS. Kunwi ur tesfunnugem"
  11,34,"Xas b$i$ a kwen neûêe$, ur tesfaydayam seg wanûaê iw, ma Ib$a Öebbi a kwen Itlef. Neppa d Mass nnwen; tu$alin nnwen $uôeS"
  11,35,"Ne$ qqaôen: \"isnulfa t id\". Ini: \"ma snulfa$ t id, lbe$wv iw i yiri w. Nek, ur ppka$ di lbe$wv nnwen"
  11,36,"Ippuweêêa d i Nuê: \"ur ippamen yiwen, d awez$i, seg ugdud ik, siwa wid illan umnen. Ihi, ur k icqi wayen xeddmen"
  11,37,"Eûnaâ lbabuô, ger wallen nne£, s uweêêi nne£. Ur iyI d pmeslay $ef wid idensen, war ccekk, ad $emqen"
  11,38,"La iûennaâ lbabuô. Yal tikelt ara âaddin $uôes imvebbôen n ugdud is, tkaâriren fellas. Inna: \"ma temmaâlkem degne$, ihi, a nemmaâlek degwen akken temmaâlkem"
  11,39,"Deqqal a ppeéôem, u$uô ara d ias uâaqeb ara t isdullen, ara iêaz uâaqeb imezgi"
  11,40,"Alamma, mi d iusa lameô nne£, la pfeggiven igwefran d ihedman, Nenna: \"awi degs tayuga n yal ûûenf, tawacult ik - siwa wid i$ef id izwar wawal -, akked wid iumnen\". Drus kan i iumnen yides"
  11,41,"Inna: \"rekbet degs, s yisem n Öebbi, acali s akked trusi s. Mass iw, s tidep, Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu"
  11,42,"Icula yissen, di lemwao anect idurar. Issawel Nuê i mmi s, i illan weêdes: \"a mmi ali d yidne$, ur teppiliv ar ijehliyen"
  11,43,"Inna: \"ûûôan iw d adrar, ad iyi isellek seg waman\". Inna: \"assa, ulac leslak si lameô n Öebbi, siwa i win i$ef Iêun\". Âaddant lemwao garasen. Iûebê ed seg wid ipwa$emqen"
  11,44,"Nnan: \"a tamurt, seblaâ aman im, a yigenni eûûfu\". Aman zzren. Iûaô lameô: irs $ef Loudi. Iffe$ uberraê: akin agdud imednas"
  11,45,"Inuj Nuê ar Mass is, inna: \"a Mass iw! Ni$ mmi n twacult iw. Ih, lemâahda K d tidep, Keçç Tifev akw imêaddan"
  11,46,"Inna: \"a Nuê! Neppa, s tidep, ur illi n wacult ik. Ih, neppa ur ixdim ayen ilhan. Ihi, ur iyI d steqsay $ef wayen ur tessinev. Nek a k Ssakwaye$, ur teppiliv seg wid ur nessin"
  11,47,"Inna: \"a Mass iw! Ili di lâawen iw, iwakken ur K id steqsaye$ $ef wayen ur ssine$. Ma ur iyi Tsemmêev, ur Têunev felli, ad ili$ seg imexsuôen"
  11,48,"Nnan d: \"a Nuê! Ers ed s tifrat s$uône£, akked lbaôaka, fellak akw $ef leoyus i illan yidek. Kra n legyus, a ten N$it. Sinna, fellasen s$uône£, aâaqeb aqeôêan"
  11,49,"Tagi si teqûivin n tbavnit, Nweêêa yak tent. Ur tent tessinev, keçç, ne$ agdud ik, uqbel wagi. Ihi, eûbeô, taggara, war ccekk, i wid ipêezziben"
  11,50,"I Âad, gmat sen Hud, inna: \"a yagdud iw! Âabdet Öebbi! Ur tesâim ôebbi, war Neppa. Kunwi tesnulfuyem d kan"
  11,51,"A yagdud iw! Ur awen ssuture$ taqdiât $ef waya. Taqdiât iw ar Win kan, iyi d Ixelqen. Day ur tefhimem ara"
  11,52,"A yagdud iw! Ssutret ssmaê i Mass nnwen, sinna, steôoâet aS. Ad awen d Isse$li ageffur d ihedman, ad awen irnu tazmert i tezmert nnwen. Ur ppu$alet d ibe$wviyen"
  11,53,"Nnan as: \"a Hud! Ur a$ d tusid s ubeggen, ur neppaoa, nekwni, iôebbiten nne$, ilmend n wawal ik, ur numin yisek"
  11,54,"Neqqaô kan, d kra iôebbiten nne$, i k i$eôqen\". Inna: \"nek, Anagi w d Öebbi, u cehhdet ar ur ppka$ ara deg wayen tepcarakem"
  11,55,"war Neppa. Ihi, andit iyi akken ma tellam, sinna ur iyi sganayet"
  11,56,"Nek, ppekle$ af Öebbi, Mass iw u Mass nnwen. Ur illi umexluq ur Iîîif seg ixef is. Ih, Mass iw deg ubrid uwqim"
  11,57,"Ma wexxôen, ni$ ssawve$ awen d ayen i$ef id ppuceggâa$ $uôwen. A d Inûef, Mass iw, agdud war kunwi. Ur T teîîuôum s wacemma. Mass iw, s tidep, d Amêareb n yal cci"
  11,58,"Mi d iusa lameô nne£, Nsellek Hud akked wid iumnen yides, s uêunu s$uône£. Nsellek iten seg uâaqeb uwâiô"
  11,59,"Akka Âad. Nekôen issekniyen n Mass nnsen, âuûan imazanen iS. Ddan d lameô n yal aqehhaô iggernennen"
  11,60,"A ten ivfeô xezzu di ddunit agi, u deg wass n tnekra. Day, war ccekk, ur jhilen ara Âad, ar Mass nnsen? Day maççi: \"akin Âad, agdud n Hud"
  11,61,"I Tamud, gmat sen ÛüÜaliê, inna: \"a yagdud iw! Âabdet Öebbi! Ur tesâim ôebbi, war Neppa. Neppa Ixelq ikwen seg wakal, Izzde$ ikwen fellas. Ssutret aS ssmaê, sinna, steôoâet aS. Mass iw, s tidep, Iqeôb ed, Ippara d awal"
  11,62,"Nnan as: \"a Üaliê, ni$ telliv garane$, uqbel aya, d asirem nne$. Day ad a$ tekksev aâbad n wayen âabden imezwura nne$? Nekwni, s tidep, aql a$ di ccekk imcebbwel, $ef wayen u$uô la $ tneccdev"
  11,63,"Inna: \"a yagdud iw! Acu twalam ma ddi$ d ubeggen n Mass iw? Ifka yi d aêunu s$uôeS. Acu ara yi isellken seg ufus n Öebbi, ma aâûa$ $uôeS? Iyi ternam, siwa taxessaôt"
  11,64,"A yagdud iw! Tagi d tal$wemt n Öebbi, d assekni i kunwi. Eooet ep a ppeks di tmurt n Öebbi. Ur p pjeyyifet, mulac a kwen id isami uâaqeb iqeôben"
  11,65,"Gezmen as ivaôen. Inna: \"zhut deg ixxamen nnwen, krav wussan. Apan lemâahda ur nepwankaô"
  11,66,"Mi d iusa lameô nne£, Nsellek Üaliê akked wid iumnen yides, s uêunu s$uône£, si ddell n wass nni. Ih, Mass ik d Uohid, d Uzmir"
  11,67,"Asu$u iwwet wid idensen, gwran d d imeslax deg ixxamen nnsen"
  11,68,"amzun ur rbiêen degsen. Day, s tidep, ur jhilen ara Tamud, ar Mass nnsen? Day maççi: \"akin Tamud"
  11,69,"Ni$ usan d imceggâen nne£ ar Ibôahim, s ubecceô. Nnan: \"tifrat\"! Inna: \"tifrat\"! Ur iâaîîel ara ibbwi d aâjmi icwin"
  11,70,"Mi iwala ifassen nnsen ur d ééilen ara $uôes, isêassef iten, iugad iten. Nnan: \"ur ppagwad, nekwni neppuceggaâ ed ar ugdud n Luî"
  11,71,"Tameîîut is tbedd, tevûa. Nbecceô ip s Isêaq, akked Yaâqub, deffir Isêaq"
  11,72,"Tenna: \"a lêif iw, day a d arwe$, nek d tam$aôt, u argaz agi inu, wesser? Ayagi, s tidep, d lwehma"
  11,73,"Nnan: \"day twehmev di lameô n Öebbi? Aêunu n Öebbi, akked lbaôaka S, fellawen ay at uxxam. Ih, Neppa d Amaâzuz, Mucaâ"
  11,74,"Mi s tekkes tugwdi i Ibôahim, u iusa t id ubecceô, inumer a£ $ef ugdud n Luî"
  11,75,"Ibôahim, s tidep, iêellem, ippanez, isteôoiâ"
  11,76,"A Ibôahim, ur keççem deg waya. Ni$ iusa d lameô n Mass ik. Nitni, a ten id ias uâaqeb, war tifrat"
  11,77,"Mi usan imceggâen nne£ ar Luî, innu$ben, ur isâi i$il a ten ifukk. Inna: \"wagi d ass uwâiô"
  11,78,"Iusa d ugdud is, zeêfen d $uôes. Llan, zik, xeddmen tucmitin. Inna: \"a yagdud iw! Atent an issi, nitenti zeddigit, i kunwi. Ëezbet i Öebbi, ur iyi pêeccimet ar inebgawen iw. Day ur illi ara, garawen, urgaz aêesbi"
  11,79,"Nnan: \"ni$ teéôiv ur nesâi lêeqq deg issi k. Keçç, s tidep, teéôiv d acu neb$a"
  11,80,"Inna: \"a lemmer i wen zmire$, ne$ sâi$ tayep ioehden"
  11,81,"Nnan: \"a Luî, nekwni d imceggâen n Mass ik. Ur k id ppawven. Öuê akked twacult ik, deg iv. Yiwen degwen ur d itezzi! Kkes ed tameîîut ik. Neppat, s tidep, a ppepwwet s wayen ara ten iwwten. Ih, ppaâud nnsen, taûebêit. Ni$ tqeôb ed tûebêit"
  11,82,"Mi d iusa lameô nne£, Nesredm ip. Nesse$li d fellas abruri n yiéôa ibelbaven n talaxt"
  11,83,"Pwanesxen ar Mass ik. Nitni, ur bâiden i imednas"
  11,84,"I Madian, gmat sen Cuâayeb, inna: \"a yagdud iw! Âabdet Öebbi! Ur tesâim ôebbi, war Neppa. Ur ssenqaset di lkil akked lmizan. Nek, wala$ kwen teôwam, u ugade$ fellawen aâaqeb, ass itezzin"
  11,85,"A yagdud iw! Ktilet, weznet, s lewqama. Ur îîuôôut imdanen deg wayla nnsen, ur pdenniset, tessefsadem di tmurt"
  11,86,"Yif it i kunwi wayen d iqqimen i Öebbi, ma d lmumnin ay tellam. Ur lli$, nek, d amêareb nnwen"
  11,87,"Nnan: \"a Cuâayeb, day a$ umôen wawalen ik, a neoo ayen âabden imezwura nne$? Ne$ a nexdem, deg wayla nne$, ayen ur a$ nehwi? Keçç, s tidep, d uêlim, d uûwib"
  11,88,"Inna: \"a yagdud iw! Acu twalam, ma ddi$ d ubeggen n Mass iw? I$at iyi yis, l$it imaânen. Ur b$i$ a kwen mgirrde$, siwa $ef wayen i wen gedle$. B$i$ kan, s wayen zemre$, ad awen ûegme$ tikli. Lâawen iw s$uô Öebbi kan. Ppekle$ fellaS, utube$ T"
  11,89,"A yagdud iw! Awer kwen teppara nnmara w d ibe$wviyen, a ppevôu yidwen akken tevôa d ugdud n Nuê, ne$ win n Hud, ne$ win n Üaliê! Agdud n Luî, ur ibâad ara segwen"
  11,90,"Ssutret ssmaê i Mass nnwen, sinna, steroâet aS. Mass iw, s tidep, Ipêunu, Ipêemmil"
  11,91,"Nnan: \"a Cuâayeb, ur nefhim ara aîas n wayen id tenniv. Aql a$ nwala k d uôhif garane$. Lemmer maççi d alag ik, war ccekk, a k neôoem. Ur a$ tezmirev"
  11,92,"Inna: \"a yagdud iw! Day Öebbi, $uôwen, yif iT walag iw, di tezmert? Terram T ar deffir n waârur nnwen. Mass iw, s tidep, Izzi i wayen txeddmem"
  11,93,"A yagdud iw! Xedmet deg umekkan nnwen, nek ad xedme$. Deqqal a ppeéôem, u$uô ara d ias uâaqeb ara t isdullen, anwa ay d akeddab. Âasset, nek, yidwen, ad âasse"
  11,94,"Mi d iusa lameô nne£, Nsellek Cuâayeb akked wid iumnen yides, s uêunu s$uône£. Asu$u iwwet wid idensen, gwran d d imeslax deg ixxamen nnsen"
  11,95,"amzun ur rbiêen degsen. Day maççi: \"akin Madian\"! Am: \"akin Tamud"
  11,96,"Ni$ Nuzen ed Musa, s issekniyen nne£, akked udabu n ûûeê"
  11,97,uô Ferâun akked imvebbôen is. Ddan d lameô n Ferâun. Lameô n Ferâun ur illi d uûwib
  11,98,"Ad izwir i ugdud is, ass n tnekra, a ten inheô ar usario n tmes. A yasario ucmit u$uô pwanehôen"
  11,99,"A ten ivfeô xezzu di tagi, u deg wass n tnekra. A tikci tucmip ippunefken"
  11,100,"Ayagi, si teqûivin n temdinin, i k d Nessawal. Garasent tid ibedden, tid ipwamegren"
  11,101,"Ur ten Nednis. Maca, densen iman nnsen. Ur ten nefâan s wacemma, iôebbiten nnsen i la naâôen, war Öebbi, mi d iusa lameô n Mass ik. I sen rnan, siwa ssxev"
  11,102,"Akka tiyta n Mass ik. Mi Iwwet timdinin i idensen, s tidep, tiyta S teqôeê, teqseê"
  11,103,"Ih, deg waya, assekni i wid iugaden aâaqeb n laxeôt. Ass nni, d ass unejmaâ n yimdanen. Ass nni, d ass n ccada"
  11,104,A t Neswexxeô kan ar lajel iuran
  11,105,"Ass ideg ara d ias, ur d ipmeslay yiwen, siwa ma s tesriê iS. Ad ilin igeswaêen, isaâdiyen"
  11,106,"Wanag igeswaêen ad ilin di tmes, s unazaâ d imeîîi"
  11,107,"ad wekkôen dinna, ayen ara dumen tmurt akked igenwan, siwa ma ur Irad ara Mass ik. Ih, Mass ik Ixeddem ayen i S ihwan"
  11,108,"Wanag isaâdiyen, di Loennet, ad wekkôen, dinna, ayen ara dumen tmurt akked igenwan, siwa ma ur Irad ara Mass ik. D tikci n war tilas"
  11,109,"Ur k ikeççem ccekk $ef wayen âabden widak. Ayen âabden am wayen âabden imezwura nnsen, zik. War ccekk, ad asen Nefk amur nnsen, ur inqis"
  11,110,"Ni$, s tidep, Nefka Tazmamt i Musa. Mgarraden fellas. Lemmer ur d izwar ara wawal s$uô Mass ik, yili useyyi garasen. Haaten, ih, di ccekk imcebbwel fellas"
  11,111,"War ccekk, akken ma llan, ad Ikafi Mass ik igiten nnsen, s lmizan. Neppa, s tidep, Issen ayen xeddmen"
  11,112,"Ihi, ili d uwqim, akken i k ippunefk lameô, keçç akked wid isteôoâen yidek. Ur be$wvet. Neppa, s tidep, Ipwali ay txeddmem"
  11,113,"Ur pqeôôibet ar wid idensen, a kwen tnal tmes! Ur tesâim bab, war Öebbi, ihi, ur tepwasellkem"
  11,114,"èéal ûbeê, tameddit, kra n lewqat n yiv. S tidep, ise$iyen neqqven tucmitin. Ayagi d asmekti i wid ismektayen"
  11,115,"Eûbeô! Öebbi, s tidep, ur Iveggiâ taqdiât n lâuûam"
  11,116,"A lemmer llan, di tsuta i kwen id izwaren, imezgiyen ineqqven asefsed di tmurt! Qlilit kan seg wid Nsellek segsen. Wid idensen ddan akked wayen i ten izhan, u$alen d ibe$wviyen"
  11,117,"Ur Isquccu ara Mass ik timdinin, d aêerfi, ma llan imezda$ nnsent d lâuûam"
  11,118,"Lemmer i S ihwi i Mass ik, ad Irr imdanen d yiwen n lois. Zgan mgarraden"
  11,119,"Kkes ed wid i$ef Iêun Mass ik. Ixelq iten i wayagi. Itam wawal n Mass ik: \"ad Acaôe$ Loahennama, war ccekk, s leonun akked yimdanen mejmulen"
  11,120,"Ayen akw i k ed Neêka n tmucuha imazanen, iwakken a Ntebbet ul ik, yissent. Id iusan dagi d tidep, d anabi u d asmekti i lmumnin"
  11,121,"Ini i wid ur numin ara: \"xedmet ay tzemrem, nekwni s tidep, la nxeddem"
  11,122,"Gganit, nekwni la nepgani"
  11,123,"N Öebbi tabavnit n tmurt akked igenwan. £uôeS ara u$alen akw lumuô. Ihi, âabed iT, ppkel fellaS. Ur I$effel ara Mass ik, $ef wayen txeddmem"
  12,1,Alô. Wigi d issekniyen n Tazmamt ipbegginen
  12,2,"Ih, Nessader it id d Leqwôan, s taâôabt, amar a pfehmem"
  12,3,"Nekwni Nêekku yak tiêkayin igerzen mavi, deg wayen i k Nweêêa di Leqwôan agi, xas telliv, uqbel is, seg wid istehzan"
  12,4,"Mi inna Yusef i baba s: \"a baba! Nek wala$ mrawyan itran, iîij, akked waggur, wala$ ten knan iyi"
  12,5,"Inna: \"a mmi! Ur êekku ayen twalav i watmaten ik, ad ak andin ticeôkep. Cciîan, s tidep, d acengu n ûûeê n umdan"
  12,6,"Akka, a k Ifren Mass ik, u ak Isselmed asefru n temsal, u ad Itim l$it iS, i keçç akked twacult n Yaâqub, akken it Itam, zik, af lejdud ik: Ibôahim akked Isêaq. Mass ik, s tidep, d Amusnaw, d Uûwib"
  12,7,"Ni$, di Yusef akked watma s, illa ussekni i wid isteqsayen"
  12,8,"Mi nnan: \"war ccekk, ifen a$, Yusef akked gma s, akken iten iêemmel babat nne$, u nekwni d îîeôma. Babat nne$, s tidep, haat di ttelfan n ûûeê"
  12,9,"En$et Yusef, ne$ nfut ep si tmurt, a d ilhu degwen babat wen, sinna, a ppu$alem d imdanen ixeddmen ayen ilhan"
  12,10,"Inna win d immeslayen, degsen: \"ur neqqet Yusef, veggôet ep ar lqaâa n wannu. Ma tgam akka, a t iddem yiwen umsebrid"
  12,11,"Nnan: \"a babat nne$, acu k iu$en, ur a$ tuminev ara, $ef Yusef. Nekwni, fellas, s tidep, d unûiêen"
  12,12,"Sseddu t yidne$ azekka, ad izhu, ad iurar. Nekwni, war ccekk, a nêareb fellas"
  12,13,"Inna: \"nek, s tidep, $weble$ ma tebbwim t yidwen, ugade$ a t içç lweêc, kunwi testehzam degs"
  12,14,"Nnan: \"ma içça t lweêc, u nekwni d îîeôma, s tidep a nili d imexsuôen"
  12,15,"Mi t bbwin, mwafaqen a t rôen ar lqaâa n wannu, Nweêêa yas: \"ad asen temlev, s tidep, lameô agi nnsen, nitni ur éôin"
  12,16,"U$alen d tameddit, ar babat sen, pprun"
  12,17,"Nnan: \"a babat nne$, s tidep, nôuê a nemzizzel, neooa Yusef ar lqecc nne$, içça t lweêc. Ur a$ teppamnev, xas nenna d tidep"
  12,18,"Bbwin d tasedrit is, degs idamen n rrya. Inna: \"xaîi! D iman nnwen i wen d iccacven lameô. Ilha ûûbeô. Anuju $eô Öebbi, mgal ayen d teêkam"
  12,19,"Usan d iminigen, uznen win id ippagwmen, issader ssvel is. Inna: \"a lxiô, wagi d aqcic\"! Ffren t, amzun d sselâa. Öebbi Iéôa acu xeddmen"
  12,20,"Zzenzen t, s ôôxa, s kra iûuôdiyen. Ur as fkin ara azal"
  12,21,"Inna, i tmeîîut is, Umaûôi i t iu$en: \"eôêeb yis, amar ad a$ infaâ, at nerr d mmit nne$\". Akka ay Nesseqâad Yusef di tmurt, iwakken ad as Nesseêfev asefru n temsal. Öebbi d Amezwaru s lameô iS, maca tegwti n medden ur éôin ara"
  12,22,"Mi d immeêtel, Nefka yas ûûwab, tussna. Akka ay Nepkafi iâaôviyen"
  12,23,"Teb$a t tin u$ur izde$. Terra tibbura, u tenna: \"eyya keçç\"! Inna: \"ad iyi Ineooi Öebbi! Ni$ bab iw iôêeb yissi. S tidep, ur rebêen imednas"
  12,24,"S tidep, teb$a t, u neppa ib$a p, lemmer ur iwala ara atebbet n Mass is. Akka, iwakken a Nessebâad fellas tuccva, lâaô. Neppa, s tidep, seg imdanen nne£ izedganen"
  12,25,"Uzzlen ar tebburt, tcerreg as tasedrit is, si zdeffir. Mmugren, argaz is, ar tebburt. Tenna: \"acu ay d aqeîîi n win iâabwlen ad iccmet tawacult ik, siwa lêebs ne$ aâaqeb aqeôêan"
  12,26,"Inna: \"d neppat iyi ib$an\". Icuhhed ed yiwen unagi si twacult is: \"ma teqqeôs tsedrit si zdat, tenna d tidep, u neppa d akeddab"
  12,27,"Ma teqqeôs tsedrit si zdeffir, teskaddeb, u neppa seg at tidep"
  12,28,"Mi iwala teqqeôs tsedrit si zdeffir, inna: \"ayagi, war ccekk, si nncub nnkwent. Ih, nncub nnkwent d timeqwôaêanin"
  12,29,"A Yusef, ppu ayagi, u kem ssuter ssmaê ubekkav im. Kem, s tidep, teccvev"
  12,30,"La qqaôent tlawin, di temdint: \"tameîîut umdebbeô têemmel acrik is. Teshebl ip tayri. F akken nwala, appan, s tidep, di ttelfan n ûûeê"
  12,31,"Mi tesla s nncub nnsent, tuzen $uôsent, thegga yasent tanalt. I yal yiwet segsent, tefka tafrut. Tenna: \"effe$ ed garasent\". Mi t walant, isdehc itent, jerêent ifassen nnsent, nnant: \"êaca Öebbi, wagi maççi d amdan, wagi siwa d lmelk ukyis"
  12,32,"Tenna: \"d wagi i$ef iyi tlummemt. Ih, b$i$ t, neppa iqqim zeddig. Ma ur ixdim ara ay s umôe$, war ccekk, ad ipwaêbes, ad ipwaêqeô"
  12,33,"Inna: \"a Mass iw! Smenyafe$ lêebs i wayen u$ur iyi d ssawalent. Ma ur Tesbaâdev ara felli nncub nnsent, ad male$ $uôsent, ad ili$ seg wid ur nessin"
  12,34,"Ijaweb as d Mass is. Issebâad fellas nncub nnsent. Neppa, s tidep, Issel, d Amusnaw"
  12,35,"Sinna, mi ten usan issekniyen, ufan, war ccekk, ilaq a t irr ar lêebs, kra n tallit"
  12,36,"Kecmen yides, ar lêebs, sin ilmeéiyen. Inna yiwen degsen: \"nek wala$ iman iw, la teééme$ ccôab\". Inna d wayev: \"nek wala$ iman iw, la ppawi$ a$ôum $ef uqeôôu w, la teppen segs ifrax. Ssefru ya$ p id. Ih, nwala k seg iâaôviyen"
  12,37,"Inna: \"seg wayen iyi ss$eô Mass iw, ad awen p id ssefru$, uqbel a kwen id iawev lqut i wen ppakken. Nek ooi$ ddin n ugdud ur numin s Öebbi, u nitni nekôen laxeôt"
  12,38,"Ddi$ d ddin n lejdud iw: Ibôahim, Isêaq akked Yaâqub. Ur a$ ippunefk a nezdukkel acemma i Öebbi. Ayagi si lfevl n Öebbi fellane$, akw $ef imdanen. Maca, tegwti n yimdanen ur snemmiren"
  12,39,"A yimeddukwal iw n lêebs, menyif imawlan imfaôaqen, ne$ Öebbi Yiwen, Aqehhaô"
  12,40,"Ay tâabdem, war Neppa, d ismawen kan i sen tefkam, kunwi akked imezwura nnwen. Ur asen d Issers ara Öebbi kra udabu. Lêukm ar Öebbi kan. Iumeô ed ur tâabdem, siwa Neppa. D wagi ay d ddin uûwib, maca tegwti n yimdanen ur ssinen"
  12,41,"A yimeddukwal iw n lêebs, wanag yiwen degwen ad ismiri ccôab, i bab is, wayev ad ippusemmeô $ef umidag, ifrax ad nneqben aqeôôu s. Ippuseyya lameô $ef wayen iyi d testeqsam"
  12,42,"Inna i win iêûa ad islek, segsen: \"ar bab ik, smekti iyi d\". Cciîan iseppu t, ur t id ismekti ar bab is. Irna, di lêebs, kra iseggwasen"
  12,43,"Inna ugellid: \"nek wala$ ûa testan tiqebwaniyin, la tent teppent ûa tuvâifin, akked ûa tyedrin tizegzawin, tiyav d tiqquôanin. A yimvebbôen, ssefrut iyi d targit, ma tellam seg wid issefruyen tirga"
  12,44,"Nnan: \"d tirga iwlellsen. Ur nelli d imusnawen i usefru n tirga"
  12,45,"Win i isellken si sin nni, armi tallit id immekti, inna: \"nek, ad awen d awi$ asefru ines, aznet iyi"
  12,46,"A Yusef, bab n tidep, ssefru ya$ d: ûa testan tiqebwaniyin, la tent teppent ûa tuvâifin, akked ûa tyedrin tizegzawin, tiyav d tiqquôanin. Amar, ma u$ale$ ar imdanen, amar ad éôen"
  12,47,"Inna: \"zerâat ûa iseggwasen imyevfaôen. Ayen tzerâam, eooet ep di tyedrin is, siwa cwiî ara teççem"
  12,48,"Sinna, deffir sen, a d asen ûa iwaâôen. Ad ççen ayen i sen theggam siwa cwiî, seg wayen txeznem"
  12,49,"Sinna a d ias, deffir waya, useggwas n tallalt i medden, ideg ara éden"
  12,50,"Inna ugellid: \"awit ep id $uôi\". Mi t id iusa umersul, inna: \"u$al ar bab ik, u steqsi t acu ay d l$eôv n tlawin i ijerêen ifassen nnsent. Mass iw, s tidep, Issen nncub nnsent"
  12,51,"Inna: \"acu ara d tinimt mi teb$amt Yusef\"? Nnant: \"êaca Öebbi, ur nufi $uôes tuccva\". Tenna d tmeîîut umvebbeô: \"tura, a d tban tidep. D nek i t ib$an, ma d neppa, s tidep, d bab n tidep"
  12,52,"Akka, iwakken ad iéeô ur t xdiâa$ ara s tuffra. Öebbi ur Inehhu nncub n lxeyyan"